quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,"Mede (Soro abͻfoͻ) a wato santen (resom Nyame),"
  37,2,"Ne wͻn a wͻde anibereε bͻ kͻkͻ. (Anaasε) Soro abͻfoͻ a wͻka mununkum so wͻ kwan pa soͻ,"
  37,3,"Ne wͻn a wͻkenkan Afutusεm no, di nse sε:"
  37,4,"Nokorε, mo Wura Nyankopͻn, Ɔyε baako."
  37,5,"Ɔsoro ne asaase ne deε εwͻ ne mmienu mfimfii Wura, ne apueε ahodoᴐ no Wura ."
  37,6,"Nokorε sε Yεde nsoromma fε asiesie ͻsoro a εwͻ wiase no."
  37,7,"Na εwεn ͻbonsam soͻdeni biara."
  37,8,"Wͻnte (ͻsoro abͻfoͻ) badwa a εkorͻn no mu nsεm, efrisε, yεto (nsoromma) fri bea biara de bͻ wͻn,"
  37,9,"depam wͻn, na wͻn wͻ daa asotwee."
  37,10,"Mmom nea ͻbɛwiawia ne ho ahwim biribi no, egya a εhyerεn bɛdi n’akyi."
  37,11,"Enti bisa wͻn sε, wͻn mmͻeε na εyε den anaasε (abͻdeε nkaeε) a Yɛabͻ noa? Yεbͻͻ wͻn firi dɔteε a ɛsɔ twann mu."
  37,12,"Nokorε sε (Nkͻmhyεni), εyε wo nwanwa (sε saa nkorͻfoͻ no ani tua Nyankopͻn tumi nanso wͻnnye nnie) na wͻredi (wo ne Qur’aan ho) fεw."
  37,13,"Sε yɛtu wͻn fo a wͻntere fo, (anaa wͻnfa afutuo no nyε adwuma)."
  37,14,"Sε wͻhunu nsεnkyerεnee bi (firi Nyankopͻn hͻ a) wͻde di fεw."
  37,15,"Deε wͻka ara ne sε: “Woi deε εyε nkonyaa anaa naadaasεm pefee."
  37,16,"Ɛdeεn! Sε yɛwu na yεyε mfuturo ne nnompe a yεbεsan anyane (bio)?"
  37,17,"Anaasε yεn agyanom tetefoͻ no nso?”"
  37,18,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: ”Aane! Na yεbεbrε mo ase agu mo anim ase."
  37,19,"Ɛbεyε nteamu fua pε, na wobɛhunu sε wͻrehwε (Wusͻreε da no)’’."
  37,20,"Wͻbεka sε: “Adi ayε yεn! Akatua da no nie!"
  37,21,"Woi ne Asenida no a mofaa no nkontomposεm no."
  37,22,"(Yεbεka akyerε Soro abͻfoͻ no sε): “Momoaboa wͻn a wͻyεε bͻne no ne wͻn ahokafoɔ (a wɔwɔ abonsamfoɔ no mu) ne deε wͻsomeε--"
  37,23,"– Wͻ Nyankopͻn akyi no ano, na monkyerε wͻn kwan nkͻ Amanehunu gya no ho."
  37,24,"Moma wͻn nyina hͻ, nokorε sε wͻn wͻ nsεmmisa."
  37,25,"Ɛdeεn na εha mo a (afei deε) mommoa mo ho mo ho (sεdeε na moyε no wͻ wiaseε no?)"
  37,26,"Daabi, saa Da no wͻbεberε wͻn ho ase."
  37,27,"Wͻbεdane wͻn ho ahwε wͻn ho wͻn ho anim abisa-bisa,"
  37,28,"Wͻbεka sε: ”Mo na na mofiri nifaso (anaasε na mo ne mpanimfoͻ a) moba yεn hͻ (bɛtu yεn fo bͻne)."
  37,29,"(Wͻn mu mpanimfoͻ no nso) bɛbua wͻn sε: “Daabi, moara nso na monyε agyidiefoͻ,"
  37,30,"Na yɛnni tumi biara wͻ mo so, Daabi, na moara nso moyε nnipa atuateεfoͻ."
  37,31,"Enti yɛ Wura Nyankopͻn asεm no ayε nokorε atia yεn; nokorε sε yεbεka (asotwee no) ahwε."
  37,32,"Nea enti yεyeraa mo ne sε, na yεn ara nso yɛayera."
  37,33,"Nokorε sε saa Da no, wͻbεkyε asotwee no, (anaasε obiara bɛnya ne kyεfa sɛdeɛ ne dwuma bɔne a odiiɛ teɛ)."
  37,34,"Nokorε sε saa na Yεde bεyε abͻneεfoͻ no."
  37,35,"Nokorε sε, na yεka kyerε wͻn sε Awurade foforͻ biara nni hͻ ka Nyankopͻn ho a, na wɔreyε ahomasoͻ."
  37,36,"Deɛ wͻka ne sε: “Yɛnnyae y’abosom mɛdi odwontofoͻ bͻdamfoͻ yi akyi? “"
  37,37,"Daabi, (Muhammad) de Nokorε no aba a ͻde bεhyε asomafoͻ no (nsεm) no mma."
  37,38,"Nokorε sε mobεka asotwee yaaya no ahwε."
  37,39,"Dwuma a modiiε ho na yεretua mo so ka."
  37,40,"Mmom Nyankopͻn nkoa nokorεfoͻ no deε,"
  37,41,"Saa nkorͻfoͻ no na wͻbɛnya akͻnhoma a yɛahyehyε ato hͻ no—"
  37,42,"(Ebi ne) Nnuaba; na yεbεhyε wͻn animuonyam –"
  37,43,"Wͻ anigyeε Aheman no mu -"
  37,44,"Wͻbεtena Ahennwa a (ebi) hwε (ebi) anim so."
  37,45,"Nsa kuruwa a efri nsuo aniwa mu bɛdi wͻn so akͻneaba."
  37,46,"(Ɛyε) fitaa, dεdεεdε ma wͻn a wͻnom."
  37,47,"Ɛmma wͻn ͻhaw (tesε tipaeε anaa yafun keka anaa adwen sεeε biara) na wͻmmoro nso."
  37,48,"Mmaa nso a wͻbͻ wͻn nhwε anaa wͻn ani ho ban, a wͻn ani akεse-akεse fεfεεfε bεka wͻn ho."
  37,49,"Wobεka sε (saa mmaa no yε) kosua a yɛahwε so yie paa."
  37,50,"Wᴐn mu bi bεdane wͻn ho ahwε ebinom abisa,"
  37,51,"Wͻn mu nea ͻbεkasa no bεka sε: “Nokorε sε na mewͻ adamfoͻ bi -"
  37,52,"Na ͻka sε: “Enti nokorε sε woka wͻn a wͻgye (Wusͻreε no) die no ho?"
  37,53,"Sε yɛwu na yεyε mfuturu ne nnompe a yεbɛtua yεn (dwumadi papa ne yεn dwumadi bͻne no so) ka?”"
  37,54,"(Obi) bεka sε: ”Monnhwε (aseε hͻ)?”"
  37,55,"Na ͻhwεε (aseε hͻ) no, ohunuu no wͻ Amane-hunu gya no mfimfii."
  37,56,"Ɔbεka sε: ”Medͻ Nyame sε, εkaa kakraabi sε anka wode me kͻͻ ͻsεeε mu."
  37,57,"Sε εnyε me Wura Nyankopͻn adom nti a, anka meka wͻn a yεde wͻn baa (Amane-hunu gya no) mu no ho."
  37,58,"(Soro aheman no mu foͻ no bεka sε): “Enti yɛnwu (bio)?"
  37,59,"Gyesε yɛwuo a edikan no ara? Na yεntwe y'aso nso?"
  37,60,"Nokorε sε, woi ne nkonimdie kεseε paa no."
  37,61,"Woi sεso nti, wͻn a wͻredi dwuma (pa) no nni dwuma (pa) mfa ma."
  37,62,"(Soro aheman no mu) anigyesεm no na εyε, anaasε Zaquum dua noa?"
  37,63,"Nokorε sε, Yɛayε no suntidua ama abͻneεfoͻ no."
  37,64,"Nokorε sε (Zaquum) yε dua a efifi wͻ Amane-hunu gya no ase."
  37,65,"N’aba no pue tesε awͻwͻ ti."
  37,66,"Nokorε sε, (saa dua no) so na (abͻneεfoͻ no) bɛdidi de ahyε wͻn y'afunu mma."
  37,67,"Na akyire yi nokorε sε, yεbεma wͻn nsuohyeε a adi afra (anom) agu so."
  37,68,"Na afei wͻn nkyi a wͻbεsan akͻ ne gya frama no mu."
  37,69,"Nokorε sε wͻbεtoo wͻn agyanom sε wͻn ayera;"
  37,70,"Na wͻn anamͻn so na wͻpε ntεm kͻ."
  37,71,"Ampa sε, tetefoͻ a wͻdii wͻn anim kan no beberee yerae."
  37,72,"Ampa nso sε Yεsomaa kͻkͻbͻfoͻ firi wͻn mu (baa wͻn hͻ bεbͻͻ wͻn kͻkͻ.)"
  37,73,"Enti hwε sεdeε wͻn a yεbͻͻ wͻn kͻkͻ (na wͻantie kͻkͻbͻ no ) awieε si wieε."
  37,74,"Na mmom Nyankopͻn nkoa a wͻdi nokorε no deε, (wͻbɛnya ͻgyeε)."
  37,75,"Ampa nso sε Noa su frεε Yεn; na nnyeso pa paa na Yεde gyee (no) soͻ."
  37,76,"Yεgyee ͻno ne n’abusuafoͻ nkwa firi mmusuo kεseε no mu."
  37,77,"Yεmaa n’asefoͻ na εkaeε."
  37,78,"Yɛgyaa no maa nkyirimma (maa wͻbͻͻ no din pa)."
  37,79,"Asomdwoeε a efiri amansan so nyinaa wͻ Noa so."
  37,80,"Nokorε sε, saa na yɛtua apapafoͻ no ka."
  37,81,"Nokorε sε na ͻka Yε nkoa agyidifoͻ no ho."
  37,82,"Afei Yεmaa nsuo faa nkaeε no."
  37,83,"Nokorε sε ne nkorͻfoͻ a (wͻdii n’anamͻn soͻ) no bi ne Abraham."
  37,84,"Ɛberε a ͻde akoma pa a emu teε baa ne Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ."
  37,85,"Ɛberε a ͻka kyerεε n’agya ne ne nkorͻfoͻ sε: “Ɛdeεn na moresom yi?"
  37,86,"Nkontompo anyame na mofri Nyankopͻn akyi pε (wͻn)?"
  37,87,"Mo adwen ne sεn wͻ Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura Nyankopͻn no ho? “"
  37,88,"Ɔhwεε nsoromma mu hwεe."
  37,89,"Ɔkaa sε: “Meyare”."
  37,90,"Enti wͻdanee wͻn ho firii ne ho kͻe."
  37,91,"(Abraham) danee ne ho kͻͻ wͻn abosom no ho ka kyerεε (abosom no) sε: “Monni di?"
  37,92,"Ɛdeεn na εha mo a enti monkasa yi? “"
  37,93,"Ɔdane ne ho kͻͻ wͻn so de (ne) nsa nifa bobͻͻ wͻn."
  37,94,"(Ne nkorͻfoͻ no) de ahoͻherε baa ne hͻ."
  37,95,"(Abraham) kaa sε: “Mosom adeε a (moara mode monsa) asene?"
  37,96,"Aberε a Nyankopͻn na abͻ mo, ne adeε a moyͻ no “."
  37,97,"(Ne nkorͻfoͻ no) kaa sε: “Monsi (fononoo) dan ma no na monhye no wͻ gya tanaa no mu."
  37,98,"Wͻhwehwε bͻͻ ne ho pͻ, nanso Yεbrεε wͻn ase."
  37,99,"Ɔkaa sε: “Medeε merekͻ me Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ na Ɔbεkyerε me kwan”."
  37,100,"“Me Wura, dom me na kyε me (ͻba) pa."
  37,101,"Enti Yεde abͻfra a ͻwͻ ntoboaseε hyεε no bͻ."
  37,102,"Ɛberε a (abͻfra no) duruu (sε wanyin a) ͻbεka ne ho (aboa no) adwuma no, (Abraham) kaa sε: “Me ba, mahunu wͻ me daeε mu sε meretwa wo mene (de wo abͻ afͻdeε ama Nyankopͻn) enti kyerε deε wadwen yε woͻ. (Abͻfra no) kaa sε: ”M’agya, yε sεdeε yɛahyε woͻ no, na sε Nyankopͻn pε a wo bɛhunu sε meka aboterεfoͻ no ho “."
  37,103,"Enti εberε a wͻn mmienu brεε wͻn ho ase (maa Nyankopͻn ahyεdeε), na (Abraham) de no too hͻ wͻ (ne) momasoͻ no,"
  37,104,"Yεfrεε no sε: “Abraham!"
  37,105,"Nokorε sε wadi yikyerε no so. Nokorε sε saa ara na Yɛtua apapafoͻ no ka."
  37,106,"Nokorε sε woi yε nsͻhwε a εda adi pefee"
  37,107,"Na Yεde afͻrebᴐ deε kεseε bi (odwan paa a otua dua) sii n’anan,"
  37,108,"Na yɛgyaa no de maa nkyirimma (maa wͻbͻͻ no din pa)."
  37,109,"Asomdwoeε wͻ Abraham so."
  37,110,"Saa ara na Yɛtua apapafoͻ no ka."
  37,111,"Nokorε sε (Abraham) ka Yε nkoa agyidiefoͻ no ho."
  37,112,"Yεde Is’haaq, nkͻmhyεni a ͻka apapafoͻ no ho no (awoͻ ho) bᴐhyԑ maa no."
  37,113,"Na Yɛhyiraa no ne Is’haaq. Wͻn asefoͻ no mu, na ebi yε apapafoͻ, na ebinom nso yεε bͻne sisii wͻn ho pefee."
  37,114,"Nokorε sε Yεde Y’adom dom Mose ne Aaron."
  37,115,"Na Yεgyee wͻn mmienu ne wͻn nkorͻfoͻ firi ͻhaw kεseε no mu,"
  37,116,"Na Yεboaa wͻn maa wͻbεyεε nkonimdifoͻ,"
  37,117,"Na Yεde Nwoma pefee no maa wͻn mmienu."
  37,118,"Na Yεkyerεε wͻn mmienu kwan tenenee no."
  37,119,"Na Yɛgyaa wͻn de maa nkyirimma (maa wͻbͻͻ wͻn din pa)."
  37,120,"Asomdwoeε wͻ Mose ne Aaron so."
  37,121,"Nokorε sε saa ara na Yɛtua apapafoͻ no ka."
  37,122,"Nokorε sε wͻn mmienu ka Yε nkoa agyidiefoͻ no ho."
  37,123,"Nokorε sε, Elia nso ka Asomafoͻ no ho."
  37,124,"Ɛberε a ͻka kyerεε ne nkorͻfoͻ no sε: ”Enti monnsuro Nyankopͻn?"
  37,125,"“Mosu frε (ͻbosom) Baal, εna motwa Nea Ɔbͻͻ adeε (nyinaa) yie no gya -"
  37,126,"Nyankopͻn a Ɔne mo Wura, ne mo agyanom a wͻdii kan no Wura no? “"
  37,127,"Nanso wͻanye (Elia) anni, enti nokorε sε yεde wͻn bεba (asotwee no mu)."
  37,128,"Gyesε Nyankopͻn nkoa no a yɛayi wͻn no."
  37,129,"Na Yɛgyaa no de maa nkyirimma (maa wͻbͻͻ no din pa)."
  37,130,"Asomdwoeε wͻ Elia so."
  37,131,"Nokorε sε saa ara na Yɛtua apapafoͻ no ka."
  37,132,"Nokorε sε ͻka Yε nkoa agyidiefoͻ no ho."
  37,133,"Nokorε sε Lut nso ka Asomafoͻ no ho."
  37,134,"Ɛberε a Yεgyee no ne n’abusuafoͻ nyinaa -"
  37,135,"Gyesε (ne yere) aberewa no; na ͻka wͻn a wͻkaa akyire no ho."
  37,136,"Afei Yεsεee nkaeε no pasaa."
  37,137,"Nokorε sε motwam wͻ wͻn ho anͻpa"
  37,138,"Ne anadwo, Enti monfa adwen?"
  37,139,"Nokorε sε Yona nso ka Asomafoͻ no ho."
  37,140,"Ɛberε a odwane kͻͻ nsuom hyεn a ayε mma no mu no,"
  37,141,"(Ɔpenee so ne wͻn) twee ntonto, na ͻkaa wͻn a wᴐdii nkuguo no ho."
  37,142,"Enti adwene (kεseε) no menee no, na na ͻfata soboͻ."
  37,143,"Nokorε sε, sε na ͻnka wͻn a wͻbͻ (Nyankopͻn) abodin no ho a,"
  37,144,"Anka ͻbεtena (adwene no) yεm hͻ akosi Wusͻreε da."
  37,145,"Na Yεtoo no twenee wͻ mpoano petee bi mu a (saa berε no na) ͻyareε."
  37,146,"Yεmaa kͻntoa dua fifiri maa no."
  37,147,"Na Yεsomaa no kͻͻ (nnipa) mpem ha anaasε deε εboro saa hͻ."
  37,148,"Na wͻgye dii, enti Yεbͻͻ wͻn akͻnhoma (anaa Yεmaa wͻgyee wͻn ani) kͻpem εberε bi."
  37,149,"Enti bisa wͻn sε: “Wo Wura Nyankopͻn wͻ mma mmaa, εna wͻn nso wͻn wͻ mma mmarima?"
  37,150,"Anaasε Yεbͻͻ soro abͻfoͻ no mmaa abrε a wͻhunuiε?”"
  37,151,"Ɛnyε wͻn ara wͻn nkontomposεm mu na wͻka sε:-"
  37,152,"“Nyankopͻn awo ba? Nokorε sε wͻyε nkontompofoͻ”"
  37,153,"Enti (Nyankopͻn) pε mma mmaa asεm kyεn mma mmarima?"
  37,154,"Ɛdeεn na εha mo a mobu atεn saa?"
  37,155,"Adεn monnwen?"
  37,156,"Anaasε mowͻ nyinasoͻ pefee bi?"
  37,157,"Sε moyε nokwafoͻ ampa a, εneε monfa mo Nwoma no mmra."
  37,158,"Wͻde abusuabͻ ato (Nyankopͻn) ne Jinn ntεm. Ampa sε Jinnfoͻ no nim yie sε wͻbεba (atemmuo mu wͻ Nyankopͻn anim)."
  37,159,"Kronkron Hene ne Nyankopͻn, (Ne ho te) sε wͻde biribi susu no no."
  37,160,"Gyesε Nyankopͻn nkoa a wᴐdi nokorԑ no."
  37,161,"Enti nokorε sε, (abosomsomfoͻ), mone deε mosom no (nyinaa) -"
  37,162,"-Montumi nyε suntidua (anaa montumi nyera obiara mma) entia Nyankopͻn,"
  37,163,"Gyesε obi a (yɛahyehyε sε) ͻbεhye wͻ gya frama no mu."
  37,164,"Yԑn (soro abͻfoͻ), yԑn mu biara wᴐ bea bi a yɛahyehyԑ ama no."
  37,165,"Nokorε sε yεto santen (frε Nyame)."
  37,166,"Nokorε nso sε yεn na yεbͻ (Nyankopͻn) abodin paa."
  37,167,"Na (abosomsomfoͻ no) ka sε:"
  37,168,"“Sε yɛnyaa Afutusεm tesε tetefoͻ no a,"
  37,169,"Anka yεbεyε Nyankopͻn asomfoᴐ nokorεfoͻ no mu bi “."
  37,170,"Nanso (afei a Qur’aan aba wͻn hͻ no nso) wͻnnye nni, enti sεdeε εteε biara no wͻbɛhunu."
  37,171,"Nokorε sε Y’asεm adikan akͻ Yε nkoa Asomafoͻ no hͻ"
  37,172,"Sε, nokorε wͻbɛnya mmoa."
  37,173,"Nokorε nso sε Y’asraafoͻ no na wͻbɛdi nkonim."
  37,174,"Enti (Nkͻmhyεni), twe wo ho firi wͻn ho kͻpem εberε bi."
  37,175,"Na wodeε hwε wͻn, na wͻbɛhunu (asotwee no)."
  37,176,"Enti Y’asotwee na wͻrepε no ntεm no?"
  37,177,"Sε esiane ba wͻn fie adihͻ a, εbεyε anͻpa bͻne ama wͻn a yɛabͻ wͻn kͻkͻ no."
  37,178,"Enti wodeε twe wo ho firi wͻn ho kͻpem εberε bi,"
  37,179,"Na wodeԑ hwε, na εnkyε koraa w’bɛhunu (asotwee no)."
  37,180,"Kronkron Hene ne wo Wura Nyankopͻn, Tumi ne Animuonyam Wura ne no (Ne ho te sen) sεdeε wͻsusu no no."
  37,181,"Asomdwoeε wͻ asomafoͻ no so."
  37,182,"Aseda no wͻ Nyankopͻn, abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no."
